Class BabaElement

java.lang.Object
BabaElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
BabaEntity, java.lang.Comparable<BabaEntity>
public class BabaElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements BabaEntity
BabaElement defines element ( rock, baba, wall...). This class is characterized by the following information :
  • The type of the Element defined with a NounImgEnum
  • A list of rule, defined as a list of PropertyEnum
  • A list of coordinates, defined as a list of Coordinate
BabaElement manages for an element, where is he (his coordinates), his rules and the comparison between another BabaElement
